HEADWORD: Seedtime
<hw>Seed"time`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>s⟦aemac⟧dt⟦imac⟧ma</ets>.]</ety> <def>The season proper for
