[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>While the earth remaineth, <qex>seedtime</qex> and harvest, and
cold and heat, and summer and winter, and day and night, shall not
cease.</q> <rj><qau>Gen. viii. 22.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

